{"tid":1660203,"cid":5,"subCid":12,"title":"TWITTER 要人!!! 咁多外國勢力幫香港人幫到盡, 你地比D 表示支持得唔得呀!?","createTime":"2019-10-17T11:23:37.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-18T05:09:31.000Z","uid":157411,"like":25,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":23,"replies":[{"pid":"0e5a007467309cc51d7364ae0acbc3464e5dfb4c","tid":1660203,"uid":157411,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-17T11:23:37.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://twitter.com/gurimelby/status/1184397534917214210\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fgurimelby%2Fstatus%2F1184397534917214210&d=vw1niP5YtVVR3vfDaqqaARzw8eMAegQd4vHbNIzLZr4%3D&h=55092668\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fgurimelby%2Fstatus%2F1184397534917214210&h=9dd48413\" target=\"_blank\">https://twitter.com/gurimelby/status/1184397534917214210</a><br />\n挪威議員Guri Melby出到聲提名香港人拎諾貝爾都係得2.4K 個RT 同 5.1K 個LIKE<br />\n究竟D 和理非去晒邊?<br />\n<br />\n仲有以下呢堆美國大佬, 雖然眾議院過左姐, 你都多謝下人地呀<br />\n你想參議院PASS 埋都比D 表示支持下呀, 兩三萬RT 都上唔到?<br />\n你地有冇搞撚錯呀!?<br />\nBryan Steil<br />\n@RepBryanSteil<br />\n<a href=\"https://twitter.com/RepBryanSteil/status/1184216398953943040\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FRepBryanSteil%2Fstatus%2F1184216398953943040&d=vw1niP5YtVVR3vfDaqqaARzw8eMAegQd4vHbNIzLZr4%3D&h=9c004264\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FRepBryanSteil%2Fstatus%2F1184216398953943040&h=6ffea6cb\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://twitter.com/RepBryanSteil/status/1184216398953943040</a><br />\n<br />\nRep. Russ Fulcher<br />\n@RepRussFulcher<br />\n<a href=\"https://twitter.com/RepRussFulcher/status/1184493685255352320\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FRepRussFulcher%2Fstatus%2F1184493685255352320&d=vw1niP5YtVVR3vfDaqqaARzw8eMAegQd4vHbNIzLZr4%3D&h=d0d38a20\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FRepRussFulcher%2Fstatus%2F1184493685255352320&h=55fc5ad4\" targ